    "# üèÄ Analyse des Blessures NBA ‚Äî 2010‚Äì2020\n",
    "Ce notebook reproduit l‚Äôanalyse compl√®te d√©crite dans ton rapport PDF. L‚Äôobjectif est de recr√©er :\n",
    "- un **dataset r√©aliste simul√©**\n",
    "- une **classification des blessures**\n",
    "- un **score de gravit√© pond√©r√©**\n",
    "- des **analyses temporelles et par √©quipe**\n",
    "- des **insights cl√©s**\n",
    "\n",
    "> ‚ö†Ô∏è Les donn√©es ci-dessous sont g√©n√©r√©es artificiellement car le dataset r√©el n‚Äô√©tait pas fourni. Elles respectent les tendances et distributions observ√©es dans ton analyse PDF."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f1299182",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. Import des biblioth√®ques"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "f0108f5b",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import pandas as pd\n",
    "import numpy as np\n",
    "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
    "import seaborn as sns\n",
    "\n",
    "%matplotlib inline"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b0a5f02c",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. G√©n√©ration d‚Äôun dataset NBA r√©aliste\n",
    "On g√©n√®re 12 000 enregistrements couvrant :\n",
    "- saisons 2010‚Äì2020\n",
    "- 30 √©quipes\n",
    "- types de blessures\n",
    "- dur√©e d‚Äôindisponibilit√©\n",
    "- p√©riodes de la saison."
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "7ba903ae",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "np.random.seed(42)\n",
    "\n",
    "teams = [\n",
    "    'Lakers', 'Warriors', 'Celtics', 'Bulls', 'Heat', 'Spurs', 'Clippers',\n",
    "    'Raptors', 'Jazz', 'Nets', 'Knicks', 'Suns', 'Mavericks', 'Nuggets',\n",
    "    'Hawks', 'Magic', 'Pacers', 'Pistons', 'Kings', 'Rockets', 'Timberwolves',\n",
    "    'Trail Blazers', 'Hornets', 'Cavaliers', 'Thunder', 'Bucks', '76ers',\n",
    "    'Wizards', 'Grizzlies', 'Pelicans'\n",
    "]\n",
    "\n",
    "injury_types = ['ankle', 'knee', 'hamstring', 'back', 'wrist', 'shoulder']\n",
    "seasons = list(range(2010, 2021))\n",
    "periods = ['Preseason', 'Season', 'Postseason']\n",
    "\n",
    "n = 12000\n",
    "\n",
    "df = pd.DataFrame({\n",
    "    \"Team\": np.random.choice(teams, n),\n",
    "    \"Season\": np.random.choice(seasons, n),\n",
    "    \"InjuryType\": np.random.choice(injury_types, n, p=[0.25,0.25,0.2,0.15,0.1,0.05]),\n",
    "    \"DaysOut\": np.random.exponential(scale=10, size=n).astype(int) + 1,\n",
    "    \"Period\": np.random.choice(periods, n, p=[0.25,0.65,0.10])\n",
    "})\n",
    "\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f7bfaa05",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 3. Classification des blessures\n",
    "Selon ton rapport PDF :\n",
    "- **Mineure** : < 7 jours\n",
    "- **Mod√©r√©e** : 7‚Äì21 jours\n",
    "- **S√©v√®re** : > 21 jours"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "93086d45",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "def classify(days):\n",
    "    if days < 7:\n",
    "        return \"Minor\"\n",
    "    elif days <= 21:\n",
    "        return \"Moderate\"\n",
    "    return \"Severe\"\n",
    "\n",
    "df[\"Severity\"] = df[\"DaysOut\"].apply(classify)\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "af9de657",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 4. Score de gravit√© pond√©r√©\n",
    "Score bas√© sur :\n",
    "- dur√©e d'indisponibilit√©\n",
    "- s√©v√©rit√©\n",
    "- p√©riode de la saison (pond√©ration selon ton PDF)"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "1e045384",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "weights = {\n",
    "    \"Preseason\": 1.2,\n",
    "    \"Season\": 1.0,\n",
    "    \"Postseason\": 1.5\n",
    "}\n",
    "\n",
    "severity_weights = {\"Minor\":1, \"Moderate\":2, \"Severe\":3}\n",
    "\n",
    "df[\"WeightedScore\"] = df[\"DaysOut\"] * df[\"Period\"].apply(lambda x: weights[x]) * df[\"Severity\"].apply(lambda x: severity_weights[x])\n",
    "df.head()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "ad97cb49",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 5. Analyse par √©quipe ‚Äî Total de blessures"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "ba2d7372",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "team_counts = df[\"Team\"].value_counts().head(10)\n",
    "team_counts"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "057fbd8d",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(8,4))\n",
    "sns.barplot(x=team_counts.index, y=team_counts.values)\n",
    "plt.title(\"√âquipes les plus touch√©es (2010‚Äì2020)\")\n",
    "plt.xticks(rotation=45)\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "21407a50",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 6. R√©partition des types de blessures"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "358c5d50",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "severity_dist = df[\"Severity\"].value_counts(normalize=True)\n",
