   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": null,
   "id": "8924b425",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "plt.figure(figsize=(5,5))\n",
    "plt.pie(severity_dist.values, labels=severity_dist.index, autopct='%1.1f%%')\n",
    "plt.title(\"R√©partition des s√©v√©rit√©s\")\n",
    "plt.show()"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "c5427567",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 7. Analyse par p√©riode\n",
    "Selon ton rapport PDF, la Preseason est la plus risqu√©e en proportion."
